{"tid":2154293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大港奸 國際戰線 勾結外國勢力 違反國安法 請各位良好奉公守法嘅香港市民 切勿模仿漢奸走狗禍國殃民之行為","createTime":"2020-08-13T05:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T20:41:24.000Z","uid":23480,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2228af2ac120a55704543585c52bbdd82e0a4965","tid":2154293,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"首先，本人愛國愛港，支持香港，支持國安法，希望國家每日繁榮穩定，擊敗美國，統一地球，殖民宇宙，天朝大國千歲萬歲，永垂不朽。<br />\n<br />\n不過我近日見到有加拿大嘅港奸，妄圖勾結外國勢力，繼近日勾結加拿大國會以後，再一次企圖妄想顛覆國家，違反宇宙國安法，有見及此我決定將呢啲壞分子暴露俾大家，希望各位奉公守法嘅香港良好市民，絕不要模仿，見到呢啲漢奸走狗更加要舉報比國家，為國家校犬馬之勞。<br />\n<br />\n希望加拿大嘅愛國人士當日可以在場糾察，捉拿港奸漢賊回國受審，祝國家每日繁榮穩定，永垂不朽，千秋萬代。<br />\n<br />\n主席萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJTfJUv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJTfJUv.jpg&h=2ec54646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我睇完真係好嬲，希望係加拿大嘅愛國家人士，當日必須要出席，捉拿漢奸走狗，以下係壞分子嘅活動詳情同地方。<br />\n<br />\n以下係引述壞分子，並不是本人的想法，希望國安專員睇到可以聯絡海外領事部門，派出強力部門部隊，到加拿大捉拿叛賊壞分子！<br />\n<br />\n========================================<br />\n<br />\n香港x加拿大手足<br />\n8.16 全加拿大手足大集合<br />\n全加制裁中共. 營救手足大集會<br />\n<br />\n8.16<br />\nWinnipeg, MB<br />\n8.16 5:30pm<br />\nCanadian Museum for Human Rights<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係支香港旗<br />\n<br />\n以下係壞分子嘅面書post<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100942907924733/posts/314421429910212/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100942907924733%2Fposts%2F314421429910212%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzqnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=0c21f360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100942907924733/posts/314421429910212/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n===========================================<br />\n<br />\n@維港同心 Victoria BC Hong Kongers<br />\nVictoria, BC<br />\n8.16 1pm<br />\nParliament Building Front Lawn<br />\n<br />\n温支聯 Vancouver Society in Support of Democratic Movement VSSDM<br />\nVancouver, BC<br />\n8.16 4pm<br />\nVancouver Art Gallery North Plaza<br />\n<br />\n@Friends of Hong Kong- Edmonton<br />\nEdmonton, AB<br />\n8.16 3pm<br />\n23Ave / 111 St NE Corner1<br />\n<br />\n@Winnipeg Hong Kong Concern<br />\nWinnipeg, MB<br />\n8.16 5:30pm<br />\nCanadian Museum for Human Rights<br />\n<br />\n@Canada-Hong Kong Link<br />\nToronto, ON<br />\n8.16 2:30pm<br />\nOld City Hall<br />\n<br />\n@香港手足<br />\nMarkham, ON<br />\n8.16 5pm<br />\nKennedy Road/Steeles Ave<br />\n<br />\n@Ottawa Post-Secondary Institutions' Hong Kong Awareness Group 渥學繫港<br />\nOttawa, ON<br />\n8.16 2pm<br />\nParliament Hill<br />\n<br />\n===========================================<br />\n<br />\n屌那媽，重申，我真係好撚柒嬲，國家對香港咁好，點解佢哋啲外國走狗亡我之心不死，喺加拿大繼續胡說八道，顛覆國家，拿石頭砸國家的腳，信口雌黃說什麼:<br />\n<br />\n &rdquo;光復香港，時代革命，香港獨立，唯一出路&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n我聽完之後真係好唔舒服，希望國家可以盡快拉晒啲班壞分子。盡快回復社會安定，讓香港繼續繁榮長久發展下去。永遠支持國家在香港執政。<br />\n<br />\n希望國家光復左香港以後，可以頒返個荷蘭水蓋俾我，我唔希望國家可以比我繁榮做有錢人，我只係希望國家可以俾返個紫荊勳章俾我，證明我愛國愛黨。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝國家、謝謝主席。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257d86dd1b7679ccf7e17c2346eeb935a5400c49","tid":2154293,"uid":210794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:28:58.000Z","msg":"蝈家：好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3557681e00d3e65c307efbd698607266709caf07","tid":2154293,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:13:34.000Z","msg":"推，俾多啲加拿大人睇到"},{"pid":"8835bc71141633d86a1d50189ffea7b4dc297083","tid":2154293,"uid":286735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"428192db87b96371ba2d611647a0cc8167326b5c","tid":2154293,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:58:31.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"94564a